@startuml
!include ../_style.puml

title Container Diagram

skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam roundCorner 12

skinparam rectangle<<service>> {
  BackgroundColor #E8F1FC
  BorderColor #2C5C8F
}
skinparam rectangle<<infra>> {
  BackgroundColor #F0F0F0
  BorderColor #666666
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3D6
  BorderColor #B58900
}

actor "User\n[Person]" as User
actor "Admin\n[Person]" as Admin

rectangle "RAM-USB System" {

  rectangle "**Entry-Hub**\n[Go]\nPublic API gateway" as EntryHub <<service>>
  rectangle "**Security-Switch**\n[Go]\nRequest re-validation" as SecuritySwitch <<service>>
  rectangle "**Database-Vault**\n[Go]\nIdentity storage & crypto" as DatabaseVault <<service>>
  rectangle "**Storage-Service**\n[Go, SFTP]\nEncrypted backup storage" as StorageService <<service>>
  rectangle "**Network-Manager**\n[Go]\nMesh & ACL orchestration" as NetworkManager <<service>>

  database "**PostgreSQL**\nUser identity records" as Postgres

  rectangle "**Certificate-Authority**\n[smallstep/certificates]\nmTLS issuance & rotation" as CA <<infra>>
  rectangle "**Observability**\n[Mosquitto, Metrics-Collector,\nGrafana, TimescaleDB]\nMetrics pipeline & dashboards" as Observability <<infra>>
}

User -down-> EntryHub : HTTPS\nregister / login / health
EntryHub -down-> SecuritySwitch : mTLS
SecuritySwitch -down-> DatabaseVault : mTLS
DatabaseVault -right-> Postgres : SQL
DatabaseVault <-down-> StorageService : mTLS\ncreate POSIX user / fetch public key
SecuritySwitch -right-> NetworkManager : mTLS\nACL grant / pre-auth key
EntryHub -right-> NetworkManager : Headscale coordination\n(reverse-proxied)

User --> StorageService : SFTP\nbackup / restore

Admin -down-> Observability : HTTPS\ndashboards

@enduml
